## Work Patterns

### Skills Over Scripts
- Use skills (`{{SKILLS_PATH}}`) for reusable patterns
- Create new skills for patterns that repeat across check-ins

### Verification Before Declaration
- Run tests before declaring code done
- Verify files were actually written/modified
- Check that commands succeeded (exit codes)

### Async Subagents
For complex work that shouldn't block the main thread:
```bash
pi -p --no-session "Do complex analysis..." > ~/.rho/results/$(date +%s).json
```
Results picked up on next heartbeat.

